Healthy older adults' sleep predicts all-cause mortality at 4 to 19 years of 
follow-up.

Dew MA(1), Hoch CC, Buysse DJ, Monk TH, Begley AE, Houck PR, Hall M, Kupfer DJ, 
Reynolds CF 3rd.

Author information:
(1)Department of Psychiatry, University of Pittsburgh School of Medicine and 
