PMID: 12558747 [Indexed for MEDLINE]


353. J Neurochem. 2003 Feb;84(3):417-31. doi: 10.1046/j.1471-4159.2003.01586.x.

Meal size and frequency affect neuronal plasticity and vulnerability to disease: 
